data.subject: Ein Volk, ein Reich, ein Fuhrer
data.lyric:
As it Happened in the Past
 The Supreme White Aryan Blast
 Our Pride awaits us now
 Give a White Man

data.subject: Krscane pod gromove
data.lyric:
Kroz puteve gdje ni ptice ne polaze
 Kroz tisine koje se ne gase
 Preko Dolina do Tude Loze
 Preko m

data.subject: Zemljo pagana
data.lyric:
Moja Zemljo Pagana
 Zemljo Slavna
 I Svojom me Tamom privlacis
 Tvoj Hladan Ponos nas casti
 U vijek

data.subject: Iskra zla
data.lyric:
Preko perivoja sna u Smrti
 Gavran mi sudi
 Dok se vjetar budi
 Prazan glas sto me strti
 Ali neboji
